        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar a = parseFloat(gender);\nvar b = parseFloat(smoking);\nvar c = parseFloat(history);\nvar d = parseFloat(opiods);\n\nvar score = a + b + c + d; \n\nvar risk1;\n\nif (score == 0) {\n\trisk1 = '10';\n}\nelse if (score == 1) { \n\trisk1 = '21';\n}\nelse if (score == 2) { \n\trisk1 = '39';\n}\nelse if (score == 3) { \n\trisk1 = '61';\n}\nelse if (score == 4) { \n\trisk1 = '79';\n}\n\n//results\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: risk1 + '% 24-hour risk of PONV'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'Apfel Score'   \n    });\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'risk1',\n    value: risk1, \n    value_text: '%',\n    message: '24-hour risk of PONV'\n});\n",
